SPMT 425: Sport Analytics. 3 credits.
Discusses theories and concepts in sport analytics. Topics cover
player performance, player management, sports data strategies, team
management, and game day operations and strategies. Offered by School of Sport/Rec/Tour Mgmt. Limited to three attempts.
